examples.en: It could have sparked a major confrontation.
What was it that sparked your interest in motoring?
The unfair tax laws sparked a rebellion.
A dropped cigarette might have sparked the fire.
The police response sparked outrage in the community.
Some hot ash fell into the box of matches, and sparked off the whole lot.
Long-simmering tensions between the two groups eventually sparked violence.
Nuclear power has always been a topic that has sparked off considerable debate.
A controversial penalty decision sparked a free-for-all at the end of the match.
